__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    testEnums:
      path: /test
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: TestEnumsRequest
        body:
          properties:
            status: optional<Status>
            special: optional<SpecialEnum>
            priority: optional<Priority>
            empty: optional<EmptyEnum>
            numeric: optional<NumericStrings>
            color: optional<Color>
            role: optional<Role>
            version: optional<ApiVersion>
            mixed: optional<MixedCase>
        content-type: application/json
      examples:
        - request: {}
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  Status:
    enum:
      - active
      - inactive
      - pending
      - archived
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  SpecialEnum:
    enum:
      - value: value-with-dash
        name: ValueWithDash
      - value_with_underscore
      - value: value.with.dot
        name: ValueWithDot
      - value: value with space
        name: ValueWithSpace
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Priority: integer
  EmptyEnum:
    enum:
      - value: ''
        name: EMPTY
      - value1
      - value2
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  NumericStrings:
    enum:
      - value: '1'
        name: One
      - value: '2'
        name: Two
      - value: '3'
        name: Three
      - value: '100'
        name: OneHundred
      - value: '999'
        name: NineHundredNinetyNine
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Color:
    enum:
      - red
      - green
      - blue
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Role:
    enum:
      - value: admin
        name: Administrator
        docs: Full system access
      - value: user
        name: RegularUser
        docs: Standard user access
      - value: guest
        name: GuestUser
        docs: Limited access
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  ApiVersion:
    enum:
      - v1
      - v2
      - v3
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  MixedCase:
    enum:
      - camelCase
      - PascalCase
      - snake_case
      - UPPER_CASE
      - value: kebab-case
        name: KebabCase
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Enum Normalization Edge Cases
